Lenny Rachitsky's archive
================================================================

This software is a hackathon submission that distills publicly-released
podcast episodes and newsletter posts from Lenny Rachitsky's archive
into short summaries, key takeaways, and applied-judgment quiz
questions. Original episodes and posts are © Lenny Rachitsky and the
respective guests/authors; their underlying rights are retained by them.

Quotations stored in this repository (e.g. citation `quote_excerpt`
fields in daily content JSON files) are short excerpts of ≤280
characters used for attribution purposes alongside direct links back
to the original source. No full episode transcripts or full newsletter
posts are reproduced in this repository or its deployed runtime.

This project is a personal hackathon submission and is not officially
